flowchart TD
  S[game_task_start — mutexy · timer · NVS config] --> B[game_initialize_board]

  B --> NV{game_nvs_has_valid_snapshot?}
  NV -->|ano| SN[boot_new_game_triggered = false]
  NV -->|ne| BT[boot_new_game_triggered = game_boot_tracker_should_force_new_game]

  BT -->|true| NG[game_start_new_game · snapshot_loaded_on_boot false]
  BT -->|false| LD
  SN --> LD[game_load_snapshot_from_nvs]

  LD -->|OK| RS[game_check_resync_needed_after_restore]
  LD -->|chyba| FB[čerstvá deska / fallback]

  RS --> LOOP[Hlavní smyčka — game_process_commands …]
  FB --> LOOP
  NG --> LOOP

  LOOP -.-> LEDNOTE[Viz task_game_loop: led_is_booting → smyčka jen čeká]
